Package com.ontimize.jee.server.services.dms

Class DMSColumnHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ontimize.jee.server.services.dms.DMSColumnHelper
  • public class DMSColumnHelper
extends Object
    This class will manage all behaviour around DMS columns naming.
    From client side will be used allways configured values in DMSNaming.
    To dao side will by applied this columns transformation.
    By default same values.

    Moreove this allows to have column extensions, indicating extends columns for each dao (document, file, version, ....)
